2619:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/api/sockets.c ****  * of the loop, thus creating a possibility where a thread could modify the
2620:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/api/sockets.c ****  * select_cb_list during our UNPROTECT/PROTECT. We use a generational counter to
2621:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/api/sockets.c ****  * detect this change and restart the list walk. The list is expected to be small
2622:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/api/sockets.c ****  */
