2673:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/api/sockets.c ****         /* For !LWIP_TCPIP_CORE_LOCKING, we don't call SYS_ARCH_UNPROTECT() before signaling
2674:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/api/sockets.c ****            the semaphore, as this might lead to the select thread taking itself off the list,
